Main - Calls game to start and render through game.cpp and SDL.
Camera - Handles pixel to tile translation for itself, creates camera and contains camera settings
Game - Calls world to create platforms, handle player input, rendering, and camera positioning
Physics - .h file holds the keys to the universe
Graphics - Through which all things are rendered
Tilemap - Creates tilemap of tiles, oob error handling, and clears tile "board"
Vec - Creates Vec template
GameObject - Creates GameObjects class and handles inputs
Toggle - Handles toggled inputs

